snippet.title: ARGHH, there's a killer chasing me! | Official Trailer | A Comedy Survival Horror Game.
snippet.description:
Itch.io: https://curlyfries709.itch.io/arghh-theres-a-killer-chasing-me

Gamejolt: https://gamejolt.com/games/arghh-theres-a-killer-chasing-me/633919

ARGHH, there’s a killer chasing me! is a comedy survival horror game where you play as Adam who is being hunted by a killer in the woods. Your objective is to escape…preferably with your insides still on the inside.

Follow developer on twitter: https://twitter.com/curlyfries709
Follow developer on instagram: https://instagram.com/curlyfries709
Follow developer on Twitch: https://www.twitch.tv/curlyfries709

Attribution:
Trailer music: misanthropy - Gundatsch: https://soundcloud.com/gundatsch
Dance Music: https://opengameart.org/content/funky-house
